Privacy Policy  --Sample--
Introduction
This Privacy Policy outlines how we, [Your Application Name], collect, use, and protect the information gathered from users through our video uploading tool. Our application facilitates the automated uploading of videos to your YouTube account, aiming to streamline your content management tasks while ensuring security and privacy.

Information Collection and Use
What We Collect:

Google Account Data: We access your Google account data to authenticate and interact with the YouTube Data API. This includes your public profile information and the ability to upload videos.
Video Data: We collect the files you choose to upload and any metadata associated with those files, such as titles, descriptions, and tags.
How We Use This Information:

To authenticate you with YouTube and provide the ability to upload videos directly through our application.
To enhance and personalize your experience, ensuring efficient management of your YouTube content.
Data Storage and Security
Data Storage:

All sensitive data, including your Google account details and video information, are stored temporarily on secure servers during the upload process.
Security Measures:

We implement industry-standard encryption and security protocols to protect the data we handle.
Access to personal data is strictly limited to authorized personnel only and is used solely for the purposes described in this policy.
User Rights
You have the right to access, correct, or delete any personal information we have collected. You can manage your data by:

Contacting our support team to request access or deletion.
Using your Google account settings to revoke our access to your data.
Contact Information
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy or our data handling practices, please contact us at:

Email: [Your Contact Email]
Phone Number: [Your Contact Number]
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to modify this privacy policy at any time. Changes and clarifications will take effect immediately upon their posting on the website. We will notify users of significant changes through our website or through direct communication where feasible.
